iv class="card_image_wrap"><div class="g_visual_wrap u-position-relative u-cover-absolute" STYLE="object-position: 50% 50%;"><div class="g_visual_background u-cover-absolute"></div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cafbff6880dabe1f2342b0/67cb070cd762e25c7fa2f90f_67c556a6a90a95057f102e32_67c504a724388016e2523f9e_iStock-1432212035%252520(1).webp" loading="lazy" alt="" class="g_visual_img u-cover-absolute"/></div><div class="g_clickable_wrap"><a target="" href="/programs/policy-organizing" class="g_clickable_link w-inline-block"><span class="g_clickable_text u-sr-only"></span></a><button type="button" class="g_clickable_btn"><span class="g_clickable_text u-sr-only"></span></button></div></div><div class="card_content_wrap"><h3 fs-cmssort-field="name" fs-cmsfilter-field="title" data-wf--global-headings--heading-size="x-small" class="heading w-variant-ad34cb72-dfdf-bd78-139e-437ff43a6c66">Policy &amp; Organizing</h3><p data-wf--global-paragraphs--paragraph-size="medium" class="paragraph w-variant-7bad1b21-23d2-5ef1-6d09-92f700b15d29 excerpt">Leveraging public health research, organizing, and advocacy to create structural change</p><div data-wf--btn-main--color="green" class="button_wrap"><div data-wf--molecule-button-layout--size="small" class="button_layout w-variant-f66b9cc7-0429-3a3d-9008-401a7db5b52c white"><div class="button_text">Learn More</div></div><a Target="" href="/programs/policy-organizing" class="button_clickable w-inline-block"></a></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" class="card-newsroom-program_wrap w-dyn-item"><div data-w-id="5d9f96a6-77f1-39cb-a421-5795ff35a632" style="opacity:0" class="card-newsroom_layout"><div class="card_image_wrap"><div class="g_visual_wrap u-position-relative u-cover-absolute" STYLE="object-position: 50% 50%;"><div class="g_visual_background u-cover-absolute"></div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cafbff6880dabe1f2342b0/67cb070b4c1f280f547f011a_67c556aabbd8f7ad1e92ca5d_67c4f37ecd96a68be6c7ab3f_67a4f59488c6cb9f3c599500_Copy%25252520of%25252520DSC07924.jpeg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="g_visual_img u-cover-absolute"/></div><div class="g_clickable_wrap"><a target="" href="/programs/bridging-partnerships-strategies" class="g_clickable_link w-inline-block"><span class="g_clickable_text u-sr-only"></span></a><button type="button" class="g_clickable_btn"><span class="g_clickable_text u-sr-only"></span></button></div></div><div class="card_content_wrap"><h3 fs-cmssort-field="name" fs-cmsfilter-field="title" data-wf--global-headings--heading-size="x-small" class="heading w-variant-ad34cb72-dfdf-bd78-139e-437ff43a6c66">Bridging Partnerships &amp; Strategies</h3><p data-wf--global-paragraphs--paragraph-size="medium" class="paragraph w-variant-7bad1b21-23d2-5ef1-6d09-92f700b15d29 excerpt">Fostering meaningful partnerships between governmental public health and community power-building organizations</p><div data-wf--btn-main--color="green" class="button_wrap"><div data-wf--molecule-button-layout--size="small" class="button_layout w-variant-f66b9cc7-0429-3a3d-9008-401a7db5b52c white"><div class="button_text">Learn More</div></div><a Target="" href="/programs/bridging-partnerships-strategies" class="button_clickable w-inline-block"></a></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" class="card-newsroom-program_wrap w-dyn-item"><div data-w-id="5d9f96a6-77f1-39cb-a421-5795ff35a632" style="opacity:0" class="card-newsroom_layout"><div class="card_image_wrap"><div class="g_visual_wrap u-position-relative u-cover-absolute" STYLE="object-position: 50% 50%;"><div class="g_visual_background u-cover-absolute"></div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cafbff6880dabe1f2342b0/67cb070a783636af1c613e81_67c556a55496fa3c8c3e5dbb_67c4f37e5092307271175861_67c3588fb287cfef930a2c6f_67c1380804d994c70d5e1213_Capacity%25252520Building%25252520pref-1.webp" loading="lazy" alt="" class="g_visual_img u-cover-absolute"/></div><div class="g_clickable_wrap"><a target="" href="/programs/capacity-building" class="g_clickable_link w-inline-block"><span class="g_clickable_text u-sr-only"></span></a><button type="button" class="g_clickable_btn"><span class="g_clickable_text u-sr-only"></span></button></div></div><div class="card_content_wrap"><h3 fs-cmssort-field="name" fs-cmsfilter-field="title" data-wf--global-headings--heading-size="x-small" class="heading w-variant-ad34cb72-dfdf-bd78-139e-437ff43a6c66">Capacity Building</h3><p data-wf--global-paragraphs--paragraph-size="medium" class="paragraph w-variant-7bad1b21-23d2-5ef1-6d09-92f700b15d29 excerpt">Building the capacity of public health organizations to advance transformative health equity and racial justice practice</p><div data-wf--btn-main--color="green" class="button_wrap"><div data-wf--molecule-button-layout--size="small" class="button_layout w-variant-f66b9cc7-0429-3a3d-9008-401a7db5b52c white"><div class="button_text">Learn More</div></div><a Target="" href="/programs/capacity-building" class="button_clickable w-inline-block"></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-wf--global-section-space--section-space="main" class="g_section_space w-variant-60a7ad7d-02b0-6682-95a5-2218e6fd1490"></div></section><section class="green_color blue-shape"><div data-wf--global-section-space--section-space="main" class="g_section_space w-variant-60a7ad7d-02b0-6682-95a5-2218e6fd1490"></div><div class="u-container"><div class="issues u-grid-column-2 u-gap-8"><div id="w-node-abdf36b6-c7a3-6eaf-1fcf-8fc0008f925a-ed12959c" class="u-align-self-center"><h2 fs-cmssort-field="name" fs-cmsfilter-field="title" data-wf--global-headings--heading-size="medium" class="heading w-variant-6f397166-5769-8472-688d-d383addb3f81 title u-text-style-h3 u-mb-text u-max-width-20ch"><strong>At HIP, we build and leverage power to advance justice and equity across key issue areas that drive health</strong></h2></div><div id="w-node-abdf36b6-c7a3-6eaf-1fcf-8fc0008f925f-ed12959c" class="u-align-self-center"><div class="w-dyn-list"